Class Visit

java.lang.Object
clinic.cs213project3.model.util.Visit
public class Visit extends Object
A linked list node containing a patient's completed appointment. The nodes make up the linked list of a patient's completed appointments.
Author:
Aarush Desai, Rohan Vuppunuthula
